name: Champawat tiger
description:
Illustration inspired by the real story of the fierce tiger of Champawat (web: michelepetrelliart.com <> instagram:@michelepetrelliart).
1900 in Nepal, a tiger wounded in the mouth by a poacher began to hunt men becoming bolder and bolder. It killed more than 437 people. When nature can't take it anymore it rebels.
